														</div>
			</div>
			<div class="content" id="post-content-3562767">
									

<p>I very rarely post anything here, but this may possibly be my favorite series of tales yet. It was the Wondertainment stuff and I honestly didn't think anything would top that, but alas, here we are/were/will be. It would've been so easy for this piece to become a jumbled mess but I feel like the writing and attention to detail was superb. Heartfelt kudos to the author. I understand these can't be easy to write and certainly a project like this takes time and effort, but should I be concerned about this being finished? Not wanting to complain or anything like that, I legitimately don't know if 8+ months means the author has moved on or not. Regardless, this whole thing was a joy to read. Thank you.</p>

							</div>

								
					
