			<div class="content" id="post-content-3756336">
									

<p>THIS IS one of my favorite series, up there with We Need to Talk about 55, and It's wonderful. All of the ti.e and realities and scps that mix together to create a beautiful mess of time and space. It's great. And I love it.</p>
<p>My only question is, I want to know two things.</p>
<p>1.) What happened to the room of Xyankses? How will that play out, if at all?</p>
<p>2.) Will the people from the first project ever be saved? And can and will you link them back in some way?</p>
<p>2.) DOES THIS ALL TIE BACK INTO HIM TRYING TO SAVE THEM?</p>
<p>1.) Will anything be resolved?</p>
<p>3.) Why dies Xyank have the mark 2 installed?</p>
<p>2.) WILL I EVER GET MY LONG AWAITED CONCLUSION?</p>
<p>And thank you for a wonderful story</p>

							</div>

								
					
